readable.content: A father feeding his child on the street . A man in a black shirt and his little girl wearing orange are sharing a treat . A man is feeding a child food while sitting near a building with onlookers . A man , seated , serves food to a little girl . A man with sunglasses and a black shirt feeds ice cream to a girl with an orange dress on who is sitting beside an opened bag .
